</PARAGRAPH>

<PARAGRAPH>
Some other known mountains or elevations of the zone are: Cerro de las Mitras, the Sierra Madre Oriental -the "m" figure visible from various parts of the city-, the Cerro del Topo Chico, Cerro del Obispado, Cerro de la Loma Larga and La Huasteca.</PARAGRAPH>
